    </exercise>
    <p>
      \setbox\answerscollect=\vbox{\unvbox\answerscollect \theanswer<nbsp/><nbsp/> <m>y = e^{-x/4} \cos\bigl((\nicefrac{\sqrt{7}}{4})x\bigr) - \sqrt{7} e^{-x/4} \sin\bigl((\nicefrac{\sqrt{7}}{4})x\bigr)</m> }
    </p>
    <exercise>
      <statement>
        <p>
          Trouvez la solution générale de <m>2y''+y'-3y=0</m>,
